# ============================================================
# Supabase (OPTIONAL)
# ============================================================
# The app works fully without Supabase — MDX files are the source
# of truth. If you connect a Supabase project, search and catalog
# features will also use the database.
#
# 1. Create a project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Run supabase/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql in the SQL editor
# 3. Run supabase/seed.sql to insert initial data
# 4. Copy your project URL and anon key below
# ============================================================
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your-supabase-url
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key
